text: FC Prykarpattia-2 Ivano-Frankivsk is a Ukrainian football team based in Ivano- Frankivsk, Ukraine. The club has been featured regularly in the Ukrainian Second Division it serves as a junior team for the FC Spartak Ivano-Frankivsk franchise. Like most tributary teams, the best players are sent up to the senior team, meanwhile developing other players for further call-ups.
